{"tid":1785121,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"證據確鑿，再無借口令我唔罷食大家樂","createTime":"2019-12-16T06:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T12:34:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"55a2a6f3b3064622a69880a8988bd9244cae19f0","tid":1785121,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"昨日大約4時，中信大廈大家樂門外天橋有催淚彈，亦一度有防暴警察駐守。當時大家樂成為左唔少中彈市民既急傷站同埋其他人既避難所。當值經理突然熄燈熄冷氣，並示意餐廳要關門，請所有人離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無意間發現，想搵借口食大家樂都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40381dac6c8674359774d7011637783b1ed67a7","tid":1785121,"uid":49391,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"食大快活啦，d嘢又咪差唔多"},{"pid":"af904c6f7546803b059fc1cdbce7ec8cfc37a58a","tid":1785121,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:04:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27eaac34c66265a141bd9b8996578c6c80453c9b","tid":1785121,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f40381dac6c8674359774d7011637783b1ed67a7","tid":1785121,"uid":49391,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"食大快活啦，d嘢又咪差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:04:29.000Z","msg":"附近無啊"},{"pid":"6adfe2b95e8be8ef2373476176eb5747a81316c7","tid":1785121,"uid":57844,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"27eaac34c66265a141bd9b8996578c6c80453c9b","tid":1785121,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f40381dac6c8674359774d7011637783b1ed67a7","tid":1785121,"uid":49391,"like":4,"dislike":1,